text: Cold Tracks () is a 1962 Norwegian drama movie directed by Arne Skouen and starring Toralv Maurstad, Henny Moan, Alf Malland, Ragnhild Hald, Sverre Holm, Egil Lorck, Lasse Næss, Siv Skjønberg. == Other websites == * Category:1962 drama movies Category:Norwegian drama movies Category:Movies directed by Arne Skouen
